    This class pretends to be the Game objets and will represent one match game, it will have trials, pontuation of the game by team, centre of the rope by game, and winners.

    Server that extends the Log and will process the events of the server.

Package general_info_repo Description

The log will be the gateway to all the information of the match, games, trials, strengths of the players. It will be responsible too for write in one file with the log of the match.
